{"tid":596114,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得連登啲毒撚好痴線？","createTime":"2018-03-17T10:00:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-20T05:45:20.000Z","uid":66512,"like":319,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"2be745ec510e6cff26c0a430cca534a5b0654b52","tid":596114,"uid":66512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T10:00:33.000Z","msg":"頭先見到有個post，係個女仔落街飲個茶都比人話著得好淫，仲要影埋上網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但其實條女都只係著得好普通<br />\n<br />\n又有啲post，只要提及到條女唔係處之後，就話成班人沖哂出黎話條女係臭雞，完全唔會再有任何討論既地方，因為連登仔既邏輯就係，　你唔係處　你等於臭雞。<br />\n又話咩揀女朋友一定要處女，如果唔係同雞拍拖無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但事實上，你咁撚大個人，只要你唔係濫交，扑個野，非處女又有咩問題？<br />\n成日係到話所有女人都係雞，非處又雞，打扮出街又係雞，就黎連識呼吸既都係雞。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲又勁多post係周街偷拍女仔。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真心覺得你班連登仔好痴線啦，懷疑係街上見到個啲陰暗毒撚就係你地<br />\n而且現實既你地邊有得揀女做你女朋友呀？講到好似啲女任你地揀咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bd9ecb66d5e24c512f39a81268992f510fefe26","tid":596114,"uid":108236,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T10:02:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連燈仔不願面對"},{"pid":"c13c2a7525f7041e655784f398cf0f7ee6689f42","tid":596114,"uid":66512,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"2bd9ecb66d5e24c512f39a81268992f510fefe26","tid":596114,"uid":108236,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T10:02:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" 